title: EP.48: TOP FANTASY PICKS, 1 YEAR GIVEAWAY, PAULO VS MURRAY, JAMARR CHASE, AND MUCH MORE!
description: In this episode we detail who you should draft in fantasy football by giving you the top players to target at each position, we announce our jersey giveaway for our 52nd (1 year) episode. We talk about the Seattle feud between Paulo Banchero and Dejounte Murray as well as the friendly competition between Jamarr Chase and Justin Jefferson. Tune in to find out more as we discuss several other topics around the NFL also.
dc:creator: Griffin Proctor & Joe Jokonya
